# Customer Behavior Analysis

## Project Overview

This project analyzes customer behavior using an e-commerce dataset. The objective is to compute descriptive statistics, probability measures, correlation, confidence intervals, and distribution characteristics to understand customer purchasing behavior.

### Objectives

- Customer Age Analysis
- Spending Behavior Analysis
- Website Engagement Analysis
- Correlation Analysis
- Probability Analysis
- Confidence Interval Estimation
- Distribution Analysis

